Class AbstractValued

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.edugility.nomen.AbstractValued
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Valued, Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Name, NameType, NameValue

    public abstract class AbstractValued
extends Object
implements Serializable, Valued
    A Serializable Valued implementation that correctly implements the equals(Object) and hashCode() methods.
    Author:
    Laird Nelson
